      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REV KEN (1) has raced below best last couple, the latest managing only 4th (23.75) last time in a Mix 6/7 at Horsham. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including one win. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Better than last start and worth following up. JUNEAU SANGRIA (6) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Maiden three back before a placing at Ballarat the following run. Expected to do much better this time. AUSSIE FERNANDO (4) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when third (23.07) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Leading chance. CHARENTE JEWEL (8) generally performs well over this distance.",
